algorithm to run wasdom esp32.

Download Arduino IDE
Run Arduino IDE
Then click on a file and then choose preferences
put the package link to the esp32,"https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json",Then press OK
Click on the tools, then choose the Arduino panel, then the panel manager.
A type screen appears in the ESP32 dialog box and then press the installation process.
Click on the tools,Go to Board , Go to Boards Manage.
Click on the tools, then choose the Arduino panel, then Go to  ESP32 Arduino.
connect the ESP32 to the USB cord to the computer.
then Click on Tools,Go to  ESP32 Arduino ,
 and then choose then choose the WEMOS D1 MINI ESP32 controller
then Click on Tools , Go to port COM3,then choose COM3.
For to turn on the lighting:
click on a file, then choose examples, then choose basic, then choose blink.
Then a page press an arrow tick appears in the address bar on the left side of the upload process.
The blue light begins to point quickly or at medium speed.
